<br>
An epic monk with the best gear can outsolo an epic mage with the best gear.  Once again, it is not particularly close.<br>
<br>
I have access to a 60 monk.  I have tested the first scenario above.  I don't have my epic, so I have not tested scenario 2.  However, I have noted that a top of the line monk solos about 4x faster than I do, and I doubt the epic will increase my rate by a factor of 4.<br>
<br>
I make no comment on whether this should or should not be.  But it is the case.<br>
